te":{"pid":"0f7c484a5f05c1e523ee9f0ad7b84b5cfe381031","tid":2268781,"uid":254735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"叫哈理發<br />\n<br />\n接近教宗程度, 但係認受性問題, 各派別互不承認<br />\n呢個位置好似懸空佐好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"好似唔會亂認係哈理發<br />\n之前好似有條友認，之後被另外條友又斬頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"有個認左 比美國佬隊冧左<br />\nhe die like a dog"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個公認抵死"},{"pid":"623f010e415c776340b0149db72ad8e12c02c0a4","tid":2268781,"uid":146556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99200270d30c420e78412e3218b74c6759c36f8","tid":2268781,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"例如咩教宗，主教，傳教士？定係無既，穆罕默德係唯一，其他人最多係信徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烏理瑪是指接受過多年的教育及鑽研伊斯蘭教科目的穆斯林神職人員，例如<strong>穆夫提</strong>（解釋伊斯蘭教法的學者）、<strong>卡迪</strong>（伊斯蘭教法法官）、<strong>法基赫</strong>（伊斯蘭教法學專家）及<strong>穆哈第斯</strong>（聖訓專家）。一些人把學術身份較低的村落<strong>穆拉</strong>（接受過伊斯蘭神學及法學教育的人）、<strong>伊瑪目</strong>（領禱者）及<strong>毛拉維</strong>（高級伊斯蘭學者）包括在烏理瑪之內，另一些人則認為符合較高資格的神職人員才可以稱為烏理瑪。一些穆斯林奉行伊智提哈德作出法律裁決，不承認宗教權威人士。</blockquote><br />\nFROM WIKIPEDIA"}]}